{"tid":2056731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旅發局擬設本港不同優惠網上平台 提供逾萬個優惠","createTime":"2020-06-09T01:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T02:09:35.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"038834e0a13ccb440f22de13b2a64c648419dcfe","tid":2056731,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:56:26.000Z","msg":"旅發局擬設本港不同優惠網上平台 提供逾萬個優惠<br />\n2020-06-09 HKT 09:24<br />\n<br />\n旅遊發展局總幹事程鼎一表示，疫情導致封關後，每日出現零旅客現象，而香港抗疫功夫做得好，保持一定的經濟活動，旅遊業對本港經濟有很大貢獻，認為既然市民及旅客都不能進出旅遊，不如香港人自己當本地遊客，重新發掘本地好去處。<br />\n<br />\n程鼎一在本台節目《千禧年代》說，旅發局將設立一個網羅全港不同優惠的網上平台，將分門別類提供超過1萬個優惠。旅發局正與業界溝通，考慮是否可舉辦本地一日遊特式旅行團。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530976-20200609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530976-20200609.htm&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19mvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=3f856cbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530976-20200609.htm&h=eddb6f8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530976-20200609.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">師奶們見到有超過1萬個優惠肯定會心動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"df06b17e12dfdb123240c0eb91fec1e3ae797ee9","tid":2056731,"uid":140552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"藍店認證系統"},{"pid":"607f274f268d7dc7f35fc0f36983ff9fdc4d20de","tid":2056731,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df06b17e12dfdb123240c0eb91fec1e3ae797ee9","tid":2056731,"uid":140552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"藍店認證系統"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T01:59:21.000Z","msg":"你肯定只有藍店會加入?"},{"pid":"2a0e6cb6db972c8e1c947e00cdd63457f3ed62df","tid":2056731,"uid":140552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"